to finance all our operational

00:07:06.280 --> 00:07:07.940
activity, not only that, but

00:07:08.020 --> 00:07:09.020
above all help us to finance

00:07:09.020 --> 00:07:10.560
part of our non-current

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.620
assets, as we can see

00:07:11.620 --> 00:07:12.860
on the screen.

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:15.260
Well, because that’s what it

