the total financial needs, which

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:20.180
is much better because we have

00:07:20.180 --> 00:07:22.400
to put the partners less money,

00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:24.760
you have to resort to a lower

00:07:24.760 --> 00:07:26.240
amount of liabilities,

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:27.180
debt, etc.

